text: Francisco Ducasse (born 3 December 1996) is a Chilean competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 470 class. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean people of French descent Category:Chilean male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Chile Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
